            <div type="slide"><head>Level 1 examples, contd.</head> 
                <figure><head>Verse within a paragraph</head>  <graphic url="../media/p173.png"/>
                </figure>  <cb/>
                <egXML xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/Examples">
                   <p>... Yes, she was, to use rather a broad term, voluptuously lovely, 
                       this girl, as she stood thus conspicuously on that balcony, 
                       surrounded by plants and flowers, waving her handkerchief 
                       as the soldiers passed by, greeting several acquaintances 
                       amongst the gallant band with —
                    <quote><l>“ Nods, and becks, and wreathed smiles,</l>
                        <l> Such as hung on Hebe’s cheek,”</l></quote>
                    forming a most alluring picture to all the present passers by, 
                    excepting one individual, who at that moment crossed over 
                    the street — her father. ... </p>   
                </egXML></div>
           
            <div type="slide"><head>Level 1 examples, contd.</head> 
